Jack Jacobs https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Jacobs 0 "Indian" Jack Jacobs (August 7, 1919 – January 12, 1974) was an American and Canadian football player in the National Football League and Western Interprovincial Football Union. He was a charter member of the Canadian Football Hall of Fame in 1963.
